column5: Just got back from Nipawin. Wow, what a trip! 100 fish in five days. Not any monsters. One 11 four more over ten and over half the fish were 5 pounds or better. Yes it was cold, but well worth the trip.I will be back.Keep the line tight,Johnnie Candle
